pecially popular in America in the 1930s, 40s, and 50s."]},{"name":"Nan","meanings":["Originally a pet form of   Ann   (for the initial <i>N-</i>,  compare  Ned  ). It is now also widely used as a short form of   Nancy ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Anne MacLean was born in 1430, in Argyll, Scotland. She married John Roy or Iain Ruadh MacLean 1st. of Treshnish about 1460, in Scotland. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"1430–":"1430–Surnud","1430–Male":"1430–Surnud","1465–1516":"1465–1516","1430–Female":"1430–Surnud","1465":"1465","1430":"1430","about 1460":"umbes 1460","1516":"1516","Treshnish, Isle of Mull, Argyll, Scotland":"Isle of Mull, Argyll, Scotland","Treshnish Isles, Argyll, Scotland":"Treshnish Isles, Argyll, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland"},"fi":{"1430–":"1430–Kuollut","1430–Male":"1430–Kuollut","1465–1516":"1465–1516","1430–Female":"1430–Kuollut","1465":"1465","1430":"1430","about 1460":"noin 1460","1516":"1516","Treshnish, Isle of Mull, Argyll, Scotland":"Isle of Mull, Argyll, Scotland","Treshnish Isles, Argyll, Scotland":"Treshnish Isles, Argyll, Scotland","Scotland":"Scotland","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Scotland"},"fr":{"1430–":"1430–Décédée","1430–Male":"1430–Décédé","1465–1516":"1465–1516","1430–Female":"1430–Décédée","1465":"1465","1430":"1430","about 1460":"environ 1460","1516":"1516","Treshnish, Isle of Mull, Argyll, Scotland":"Isle of Mull, Argyll, Écosse","Treshnish Isles, Argyll, Scotland":"Treshnish Isles, Argyll, Écosse","Scotland":"Écosse","Argyll, Scotland":"Argyll, Écosse","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Anne MacLean est née en 1430, à Argyll, Écosse. Elle a épousé John Roy or Iain Ruadh MacLean 1st. of Treshnish environ 1460, à Écosse. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"1430–":"1430–Verstorben","1430–Male":"1430–Verstorben","1465–1516":"1465–1516","1430–Female":"1430–Verstorben","1465":"1465","1430":"1430","about 1460":"um 1460","1516":"1516","Treshnish, Isle of Mull, Argyll, Scotland":"Isle